cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with the problem of long-term visual localization, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves the use of neural networks (cs.LG) and self-supervised learning (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of semantic segmentation (cs.CL) as a baseline method for invariant scene representation.
